OL,6,FLeeds City Council says its highways
OL,7,Fteam is under "significant pressure"
OL,8,Fafter a tenfold increase in the number
OL,9,Fof potholes reported across the city.
OL,11,FDeputy Leader Jonathan Pryor wrote to
OL,12,Fall councillors on Thursday 12
OL,13,FFebruary saying in the first week of
OL,14,Fthe month the authority received 300
OL,15,Freports of potholes, when they would
OL,16,Fusually have around 30.
OL,18,FHe said: "Leeds has experienced an
OL,19,Funusually long spell of continuous
OL,20,Frainfall over recent weeks.
