OL,3,CCity sees tenfold increase in pothole
OL,4,Creports
OL,6,FThere have been 2,269 reports of
OL,7,Fpotholes across Leeds so far this
OL,8,Fmonth, a 279% increase compared to the
OL,9,Fsame period last year.
OL,11,FThe council has deployed all of its
OL,12,Frepair crews and extended working
OL,13,Fhours to deal with the rise in demand.
OL,15,FCllr Pryor said: "Due to the
OL,16,Fexceptional number of defects,
OL,17,Fenquiries are currently being received
OL,18,Ffaster than they can be repaired
OL,19,Fsafely.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
