OL,6,FHe said: "We are seeing more and more
OL,7,Fdamaged wheels, with the potholes of
OL,8,FLeeds that we have to deal with.
OL,10,F"We're looking at between 40 and 50 a
OL,11,Fweek at the moment of damage caused by
OL,12,Fpotholes on Leeds roads.
OL,14,F"I think sometimes it's really quite
OL,15,Fdifficult because for some customers,
OL,16,Fit's just another weight on their back
OL,17,Ffrom a cost point of view - they
OL,18,Fhaven't got the money to repair them."
