OL,6,FCllr Barry Anderson, of Adel and
OL,7,FWharfedale, said: "It's particularly
OL,8,Fbad around here because of a lack of
OL,9,Finvestment. We've got a massive
OL,10,Fbacklog and so does the rest of the
OL,11,Fcity for that matter.
OL,13,F"We're complaining, we're not getting
OL,14,Fthe response that we should be. On a
OL,15,Fdaily basis, I'm probably getting half
OL,16,Fa dozen or so complaints."
OL,18,FSteve Rowley, an Adel resident, said:
OL,19,F"You see the Olympics - the skiing
OL,20,Fgoing down the slalom - it's very much
OL,21,Flike that, just avoiding the potholes.
