OL,6,F"Local drivers - we seem to just be
OL,7,Fbeing ignored!"
OL,9,FThe spokesperson for the council said
OL,10,Fit had a backlog of #300 million worth
OL,11,Fof pothole repairs across the city.
OL,13,FA statement read: "Our highways team
OL,14,Fis working hard to address this, but
OL,15,Fwe understand more is needed. That is
OL,16,Fwhy we are looking at new technologies
OL,17,Fthat will help make repairs more
OL,18,Fefficient and better quality.
